</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C32906CA0937FF80FF22BA9FFC88A59D" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8C55410937FF80FF22BA9FFC88A59D" blockId="29.[151,1436,479,730]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="B94789530937FF80FF22BA9FFE89A5F3" bold="true" box="[197,319,666,692]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described based on thirteen specimens collected from Chinese 
<collectingCountry id="F32415D10937FF80FAE3BA9FFAEDA5F3" box="[1284,1371,666,692]" name="Taiwan" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
from July to August. We have not collected this species to date.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
